Title: An Act Changing the Name of Buenavista Elementary School in the Municipality of Magdalena, Province of Laguna, to Conrado Benitez Memorial Elementary School
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA Blg. 549
An Act Changing the Name of Buenavista Elementary School in the Municipality of Magdalena, Province of Laguna, to Conrado Benitez Memorial Elementary School
Section 1. The name of Buenavista Elementary School in the Municipality of Magdalena, Province of Laguna, is changed to Conrado Benitez Memorial Elementary School.
Section 3. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.
Approved: June 24, 1983
